      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ACTIVE MAGIC (2) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at Goulburn over 350m behind Fancy Lena (20.37) in a NG. Was a winner prior to that. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Can atone. FUSION ROSE (7) flew the lids with a fast early split last time, hitting the frame with a 3.5 lengths third (18.38) over 318m at this track and making it two placings on end. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Well placed and gets her chance. ANGEL MEG (1) is worth forgiving last start after finishing seventh (18.96) from Box 6 at this track over 318m. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Shapes as one to consider. SLIPPERY BOGAN (6) drops in distance and can play a major role.",
